# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TTS Provider — choose ONE option below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Option A: OmniVoice  (local, free, best for Vietnamese)
# Install: https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx  — see README § TTS Setup
TTS_PROVIDER=omnivoice
OMNIVOICE_ENDPOINT=http://127.0.0.1:8123

# Option B: ElevenLabs  (cloud, requires account at elevenlabs.io)
# 1. Sign up at elevenlabs.io → grab your API key from Profile → API Keys
# 2. Pick or clone a Voice → copy its Voice ID
# 3. Comment out Option A above and uncomment the lines below:
#
# TTS_PROVIDER=elevenlabs
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=your_voice_id_here
# ELEVENLABS_MODEL_ID=eleven_multilingual_v2   # supports Vietnamese

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Advanced
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TTS_CONCURRENCY=1    # parallel TTS calls (keep 1 for OmniVoice; up to 3 for ElevenLabs)
